Recommended: Freemium + Ads
Free tier (what you have now):

All 4 tools, capped at 3 operations/day
Banner ad on home screen (AdMob)
Interstitial ad after each operation
Pro tier — $2.99/month or $14.99/year:

Unlimited operations
No ads
All Pro-only features (see below)
