Replace ↑↓ arrows with drag-and-drop — use react-native-draggable-flatlist
Add a bottom tab bar — Tools | Files | Settings
Swap emoji icons for vector icons — @expo/vector-icons is already installed
Add expo-haptics — 2 lines per button press, massive feel improvement
Add AdMob — first dollar of revenue